FROM LOCAL TO GLOBAL 🌏 Beyond grateful and honored to have been featured and interviewed by @lofficielvietnamofficial 🤍 To be recognized by those who share my roots and heritage is a feeling that is truly indescribable. 🇻🇳

Through this opportunity, I had the chance to share my personal journey and unique perspective on the fashion & beauty industry, both in Vietnam and across the globe. It was a humbling experience to showcase the immense potential of this vibrant country and its people, and I am grateful for the chance to do so. Thank you, L'Officiel Vietnam, @alexfox_alexfox @hangaa_ for the opportunity. 🇻🇳💕 #LofficielVietnam #ProudVietnamese

@helmutlang SS24 - Show of the season 
🖤 If you were Viet, there wasn't a dry eye in the room on the show date. Many Vietnamese souls, myself included, welled up with emotion as @ocean_vuong's poetry graced the runway alongside the models. 
I've been an admirer of @doxpeter's work since his days at the LVMH Prize, and now, having had the privilege of meeting him in person several times, I can attest to his kindness and humility beside the immense talent and vision. I vividly remember his runway debut in 2021 with the Manhattan skyline as a backdrop, and now, with his new role as the Creative Director of @helmutlang, it's clear that this is just the beginning of many more remarkable stories to come. 
Peter, we love you and are so proud of you. 🖤
